0.15.9:
During this version tamed cats can be left in unloaded chunks until b1.8.0.8. Leaving tamed cats unloaded for this period of time will create tamed ocelots, and thus a discontinued variant of ocelots. To showcase a tamed Ocelot, you could make it sit before the changes that rendered them untameable, or you could use the Discontinued Feature Tweaks pack
