1.4.0: (Android Exclusive Version)
When you drop TNT onto a string connected to tripwire hooks on both sides and let it detonate, a ghost block can be generated. To obtain portal blocks with this method, you first have to create a ghost block inside of a nether portal frame. Then you have to add a pressure plate that is connected to a piston responsible for pushing the player in front of the portal. Additionally, connect the pressure plate with a dispenser that can ignite the portal. Lastly, start breaking the obsidian with a silk touch pickaxe and step on the pressure plate to break the ghost block. If done correctly, the ghost block should break right as the portal gets ignited and a portal block drops
Portal Blocks can be placed next to each other without updating
<br>


