1.12.0:
Smelting cobblestone and other items[×] changes their damage value to 32767. However, any item with a damage value of 32767 will revert back to 0. You can safeguard such items by storing them in a shulker box and subsequently destroying the box. Placing the box back down would also automatically reset their damage values to 0

 - Breaking leaves with silk touch will drop leaves that don't stack with each other. These can have a "update_bit" tag, "persistant_bit" tag, or both. Just like items with a damage value of 32767, these will revert to normal leaves in newer versions. You can use the same method mentioned above to store these safely without reverting
<br><br>
