1.16.100:
If you place a gateway block on the central pillar of the end fountain and the dragon perches on the fountain, it will become frozen. Upon re-entering the end, an end gateway will appear where the dragon was, and the dragon will be free again. his exploit enables you to acquire more than 20 gateways because the game does not verify the number of existing gateways. These manipulated end gateways teleport you to the spot where you manually placed the gateway block
<br>


1.16.201:
When pushing End Crystals with a flying machine during the process of summoning the ender dragon, the crystals will not update their status. As a result, they will remain indestructible and permanently display the summoning beam
If you punch an end crystal while in the process of summoning the ender dragon, and you happen to be standing within the exit portal, you will be transported back to the overworld. As a result, you will find four beaming crystals at your exit portal, which are destructible. Please note that the number of crystals may vary, sometimes resulting in three crystals, depending on the speed at which you are sent back to the overworld

Wandering Traders sell ink sacs with a damage value of 4

Within Woodland Mansions, it is possible to obtain Leather Helmets enchanted with Efficiency 1, along with black glow sticks. The helmets can be located in a secret room containing a chest and a tree. This room is easily identifiable due to its blocked-off entrance, though the frame remains visible. On the other hand, finding the Glow Sticks can be quite challenging as they only appear in the rare Fake End Portal Room. Unlike the Helmet Room, there are no indicators to help locate it. To simplify the search for the fake portal room, you can use the Mansion Hider pack in the Texture Pack folder, which allows you to see through walls. It's important to note that both of these rooms can only appear on the mansion's first floor
<br>


1.16.220:
When a Minecart is positioned ontop of a Detector Rail and the rail is pushed, it will remain in a powered state after the minecart is destryoed

It is possible to "Flowerlog" non-full blocks. To achieve this, you need to cover a Flower or Grass with a layer of Snow and then place the desired block onto the Snow layer. As a result, the snow layer will be replaced with the chosen block while keeping the flower intact
When End Portals are activated, they do not trigger Block Updates. This allows for the creation of floating gravity blocks and other things like headless pistons and Portal-Logged blocks

By placing end portal frames across Chunk borders or adding extra frames to the corners, it becomes possible to create end portals that have missing frames. This can be achieved by flower logging End Portal Frames, activating them, and then breaking the grass block located underneath

Taking Damage mid-air right before you land will give you absorption hearts. The max amount of absorption hearts you can get is 8 and they will not disappear

Animals have a maximum speed they can walk at, but this limit can be circumvented with breeding. First, obtain 2 animals that are breedable. If the animal is a horse, make sure to tame them. Splash the animals with a potion of swiftness, and then breed them. The offspring will have a permanent speed boost. This can be repeated with the offspring to allow for even higher speeds
() - Foxes can wear armor in this version, simply by dropping it to them. If you want to make the Armor visible, use the "ArmoredFoxesV4" Texture Pack in the Texture Pack Folder.

() - Glowstone can be Dispensed onto hostile mobs that can wear armor, armor stands and players. To make the Glowstone visible, you can use the discontinued feature tweaks texture pack
