Beta 1.18.10.26 => Beta 1.18.10.22: (Android Exclusive Version, Requires Downgrading¹)
!!!   Do not turn "keep app data" on when uninstalling Minecraft because it may cause problems. Read the "1.18 Downgrade Warning for Android" Document for more info.   !!!
Downgrading a cartographer with the globe pattern trade from 1.18.10.26 to 1.18.10.22 turns the trade into an empty trade

Making a Banner with the Globe Pattern and downgrading to 1.18.10.22 turns the globe banner pattern on the banner into "item.banner.base.x". Globe Banners keep the globe banner tag, which means they will turn into normal banners when updating back. To bypass this, simply place the banners down and break them, this will remove the globe banner tag and keep the item.banner.base.x tag
